    "body" : "<p>you can use method:</p>\n\n<pre><code>BeanUtils.copyProperties(aValue, aLocal);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>in  apache <strong>commons-beanutils</strong> jar</p>\n\n<p>click here <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-beanutils/javadocs/v1.9.2/apidocs/org/apache/commons/beanutils/BeanUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">commons-beanutils</a> visit apache  document</p>\n"
